Global Horticultural Lighting Solution Market Insights
Horticultural Lighting Solution Market size was valued at USD 2.1 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 4.9 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 12.3% from 2024 to 2030.

Horticultural Lighting Solution Market Overview
The global horticultural lighting solution market is valued at approximately USD 8.5 billion in 2024, with expectations to grow significantly at a CAGR of 20.4% during the forecast period. The growth is driven by an increasing demand for efficient lighting systems in indoor farming, greenhouse production, and vertical farming applications. With technological advancements in LED lighting, the market is poised for rapid expansion, especially in regions with limited arable land and growing demand for food security. North America and Europe are currently the largest markets, though Asia-Pacific is expected to witness the fastest growth in the coming years.

